The,service,provides,updated,lift,status,for,ski,resorts,across,North,America,and,some,in,Europe,It,aggregates,a,number,of,separate,data,feeds,to,report,on,lifts,in,operation,and,out,of,service,at,selected,resorts,along,with,details,of,lift,ticket,prices,and,discounts,offered,by,the,resorts,Data,feeds,from,other,resorts,can,be,added,API,methods,support,submission,of,a,request,specifying,a,resort,name,or,a,U,S,state,Canadian,province,or,other,jurisdiction,Methods,return,a,listing,of,operating,status,reported,for,lifts,at,the,specified,resort,or,for,all,resorts,in,the,specified,location,Data,refreshes,every,seconds